examples.en: Allusive speech is characterized by allusions.
You have characterized him as an ambitious person.
His music is characterized by a happy athleticism.
This poem can be characterized as a lament for a dead lover.
Their principles of composition characterized all their works.
The storms that had characterized their relationship had died away.
His art was characterized by bursts of creativity followed by long periods of stasis.
Indian accents can be characterized by the fact that speakers retroflex their consonants
Malaria is characterized by episodic attacks of chills and fever that coincide with mass destruction of blood cells.
